CVE-2026-39852  # HIGH | quarkus-vertx-http: authz bypass via semicolons — embedded in KC 26.6.1; fix requires KC to ship quarkus 3.33.1.1 | Added: 2026-05-08 | Review: 2026-05-22

# org.bouncycastle:bcprov-jdk18on 1.83 — fixed in 1.84 (private key timing leak)
CVE-2026-5598   # HIGH | bcprov-jdk18on: private key leakage via non-constant time comparison — embedded in KC 26.6.1; fix requires KC to ship BC 1.84 | Added: 2026-05-08 | Review: 2026-05-22

